show.description: A small-town healer with secret powers enters a world of chaos, conspiracies, and cold-blooded betrayal. But in the fight for truth and love, can Henry—descendant of divine medicine—heal what fate has shattered? Dive into this gripping saga of strength, science, and spiritual legacy.
